licy\n   - `AuditPolicy` class: Declarative mapper of emitter events to audit entries\n   - `attach<EventMap>()` method: Registers event listeners that create audit entries\n   - Prevents crashes in emitter chains if audit logging fails\n\n3. **`packages/orchestrator/src/auditRetentionPolicy.ts`** - Audit retention management\n   - `AuditRetentionPolicy` class: Manages purge lifecycle\n   - Enforces minimum 90-day retention (configurable via TABLE_REGISTRY)\n   - Safety cap prevents deleting more than 80% of rows in one purge cycle\n   - Starts daily purge timer\n\n### 4. All Distinct Action Strings Used in Audit Events\n\nThe system currently logs the following 16 distinct action types:\n\n**Key Management:**\n- `key:encrypt` - Credential created\n- `key:decrypt` - Credential accessed successfully\n- `key:decrypt_failed` - Failed credential access attempt\n- `key:delete` - Credential deleted\n- `key:derive` - Tenant key derived\n- `key:access` - Key access operation\n\n**Persona Management:**\n- `persona:create` - Persona created\n- `persona:delete` - Persona deleted\n\n**Tool Management:**\n- `tool:link` - Tool linked to persona\n- `tool-definition:create` - Tool definition created\n\n**Credential/Linking:**\n- `credential:link` - Credential linked to persona\n\n**Subscriptions:**\n- `subscription:create` - Event subscription created\n- `subscription:update` - Event subscription updated\n- `subscription:delete` - Event subscription deleted\n\n**Worker Pool:**\n- `worker:connected` - Worker connected to pool\n- `worker:disconnected` - Worker disconnected from pool\n\n### 5. All Audit Entry Creation Call Sites\n\n**In `packages/orchestrator/src/index.ts`:**\n- Lines 74-76: `key:derive` (via AuditPolicy attached to TenantKeyManager)\n- Lines 78-81: `worker:connected` and `worker:disconnected` (via AuditPolicy attached to WorkerPool)\n\n**In `packages/orchestrator/src/httpApi.ts`:**\n- Line 115: `persona:create` - POST /api/personas\n- Line 125: `tool:link` - POST /ap